---
export const prerender = true;

import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | OurColoring" description="OurColoring Terms of Service">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-['Nunito'] text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#3D3530] mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-[#5A524B] text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: February 28, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">1. About the Service</h2>
        <p>OurColoring provides a free coloring page gallery and a photo-to-coloring-page conversion service.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">2. Terms of Use</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Gallery downloads are unlimited and free.</li>
          <li>Photo conversions are free up to 3 times per day (10 with email registration).</li>
          <li>The service is for personal, non-commercial use only.</li>
          <li>Downloaded coloring pages may be freely used for educational purposes at home or school.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">3. Copyright</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Gallery coloring pages are copyrighted by OurColoring.</li>
          <li>Copyright of original photos used for conversion belongs to the user.</li>
          <li>Redistribution, sale, or commercial use of coloring pages is prohibited.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">4. Disclaimer</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Conversion quality may vary depending on the original photo.</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for technical issues that may occur during use.</li>
          <li>The service may be modified or discontinued without prior notice.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">5. Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Uploading photos that infringe on others' copyrights</li>
          <li>Uploading inappropriate content (violence, explicit content, etc.)</li>
          <li>Attempting to hack or abuse the service</li>
          <li>Mass conversion/downloading using automated tools</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#3D3530] mt-8 mb-3">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms: <a href="/en/contact/" class="text-[#FF6B4A] hover:underline">Contact Us</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
